title: School assisgnment
body: Hey all, for my VCE SAC in informatics i'm doing research into whether listening to music while playing some league makes you play better. Any feedback is greatly appreciated!

replies.body:
I've noticed that when i have music playing i tilt less, which in turn makes me play better albeit inadvertently 

Alcohol also helps, 1 or 2 (standards) is enough to calm the nerves and make you focus more
This indicate you have a high level of anxiety.
